dct_title_s: The islands of Madeira : Porto Santo and Dezertas
dct_description_sm: Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. "J. & C. Walker Sculpt."--Lower right margin. "Published according to Act of Parliament ... 4th Octr. 1847." "Soundings in fathoms." Prime meridian: Greenwich. Includes 3 profiles: Porto Santo -- Dezerta Grande -- Madeira. "1831"--Lower right margin.
dct_creator_sm: Vidal, A. T. E. (Alexander Thomas Emeric), 1792-1863
dct_publisher_sm: London : Published ... at the Hydrographic Office of the Admiralty, 1847.
